version_description: The other version, while popular, contained a number of issues which have been fixed in this version. 1) the other version did not get the correct chords down for the chorus [particularly the augmented chord] 2) the other version got the lyrics wrong, particularly in the chorus, 3) the other version had the song structure incorrectly.

This is based on video evidence from YouTube. The song is played with the Capo on Fret 5. This version has the complete lyrics and rhythm guitar section (no lead). Based on her September 29th, 2012 live performance of "Soon Enough" at the Fillmore in San Francisco, Ca.

performance.name: Live at The Fillmore, San Francisco, CA, 09/29/2012
performance.comment: Live performance of "Soon Enough" from her 2012 Tour
